.Dd November 11, 2005
.Dt MACIIC 4 macppc
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm maciic
.Nd Apple Inter IC (I2C) bus
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "maciic* at smu?"
.Cd "maciic* at ki2c?"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for I2C busses on Apple
.Tn Macintosh
machines.
.Pp
The
.Nm
driver enables direct configuration of the I2C bus by using
information from OpenFirmware.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr iic 4 ,
.Xr intro 4 ,
.Xr ki2c 4 ,
.Xr smu 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver first appeared in
.Ox 3.9 .
